FPC 2.6.4irc r3.1 — Phase 10 Complete (2026-07-20)

Phases 0–10 complete. 33 bugs fixed. 7 GUI platforms + cocoa widgetset.

## Completed Phases

Phase 0–4: Build infra, 8 targets, Darwin PPUs (757), -Amacho toolchain
Phase 6a: Resource compiler (windres icons in Win32 binaries)
Phase 6b/b+: OS/2 LazUtils + LCL + customdrawn PM backend (174 PPUs)
Phase 6c: pasjpeg fixes (jidct2d, BMP types, ShowMessage)
Phase 7: Lazarus IDE (x86_64-linux 72MB + i386-win32 151MB)
Phase 8: go32v2 LCL + customdrawn VESA backend (1024x768x32K)
Phase 9: LCL Delphi backports (Ctl3D, ParentCtl3D, OEMConvert,
         CreateWindowHandle, verinfo, FPCCompat, lzmadecpas)
Phase 10: cocoa 200509189 resolved (14 PPUs) + Borland .res icon fix

