- BUG-032: Borland .res RT_ICON LangID incompatibility + fpcres rebuild
- BUG-033: cocoa 200509189 resolved (build config, not compiler bug)

## New Units

- lzmadecpas.pas: Pure Pascal LZMA1/LZMA2 decoder (636 lines, no C)
- fpccompat.pas: Delphi VCL compatibility helpers
- verinfo.pas: Windows version information reader

## Build Changes

- .gitignore deleted — use make clean instead
- build-lcl.sh rebuilt without package source paths
- fpcres rebuilt with Borland .res icon fix

## IMPORTANT: RTL Rebuild Required

BUG-034 (Wine codepage crash) patched in rtl/win/syswin.inc but
the shipped PPUs in bin/units/i386-win32/ are PRE-PATCH. You MUST
rebuild the Win32 RTL before this fix takes effect:

  cd src/rtl/win32
  ppc386 -Twin32 -Mobjfpc system.pp   (or use build.sh)

Then rebuild all Win32 binaries (ISCC, Setup, SetupLdr, etc.)
against the new PPUs. Without this step, the fix is source-only.

